20-02-27T17:27:51.000Z","msg":"又話唔會傳到比動物？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:29:48.000Z","msg":"多數check錯"},{"pid":"2ba5ea55a675bbdbe0279864371a58e668d88c08","tid":1901271,"uid":65598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:30:16.000Z","msg":"之前睇唔知咩醫生話寵物無果種蛋白去matc武漢肺炎病毒嘅 堅唔堅"},{"pid":"fc24762bcb6e879b541e9932dac1aec68ace98e8","tid":1901271,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:30:30.000Z","msg":"嚟緊九月就立法會選舉啦<br />\n五月頭就會截止登記<br />\n無論你係地區直選定係功能組別<br />\n各位手足都快啲登記做選民啦<br />\n特別係啱啱足夠18歲嘅各位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係最低成本為香港出一分力嘅方法啊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/eform/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Feform%2FREO-1%28C&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0bvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=06ee4b95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/eform/REO-1(C</a>)_eSign.pdf<br />\n<br />\n大家快啲填左上面呢份表格之後寄返去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0747a0b5f73c8524928db9cbbcadbe61183fb492","tid":1901271,"uid":126317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:31:33.000Z","msg":"香港政府治養啲狗隻呢？"},{"pid":"43d8acc81cda35c0ec119c9f89411f0008f7e051","tid":1901271,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47422d89788386f983e2c6f210e17742b6b194ba","tid":1901271,"uid":58841,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:26:25.000Z","msg":"睇標題仲以為係著住綠色制服既人型四腳狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:31:46.000Z","msg":"我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c1582a0a0b47fc26c788e45eacc11d101137b7","tid":1901271,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0747a0b5f73c8524928db9cbbcadbe61183fb492","tid":19012